_:N616b36fb9c8b4cbe8fc85867cf7dd99b <http://schema.org/description> "The Wales Office supports the Welsh Secretary and the Parliamentary Under Secretary of State in promoting the best interests of Wales within a stronger United Kingdom. It ensures Welsh interests are represented at the heart of the UK government and the UK government’s responsibilities are represented in Wales." .
